{"tid":865268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拒與中國選手握手　英國選手：他們上廁所不洗手","createTime":"2018-10-17T02:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T02:10:53.000Z","uid":35790,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5e231bf232a5988b3a0177c019e40f3ec6b0636b","tid":865268,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T02:04:29.000Z","msg":"拒與中國選手握手　英選手：他們上廁所不洗手<br />\n<br />\n建立時間：2018/10/17 07:07<br />\n<br />\n中國18歲的撞球選手羅弘昊，日前打入英格蘭撞球公開賽64強，以4:3險勝英國籍的對手達菲（Adam Duffy），不過比賽結束後，羅弘昊主動伸手希望與對手握手，但被達菲拒絕。達菲事後在推特透露，不與手羅弘昊握手的原因，是因為他認為，羅去廁所後從來都不洗手。<br />\n<br />\n達菲的推文發出後，引發大批中國網友翻牆留言，大罵他「輸不起」、「真正的失敗者」，不少人寫下中文的髒話，也有人用「中式英語」留言，質疑他是否跟著羅弘昊去廁所，看到他沒洗手。<br />\n<br />\n羅弘昊曾在微博上表示：「我肯定要投訴！」，要向世界桌球總會投訴，但後來他說，已透過微博向主辦單位投訴，可是「我英語說不通，我找這裡的負責人，但他不肯幫我去說，他覺得這件事情就算了」，感嘆自己被河蟹（和諧）。<br />\n（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181017/1448872/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181017%2F1448872%2F&d=UvGwKXXtoiGJJSbm9hgHqFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=5a4ed130\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181017%2F1448872%2F&h=1945123e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181017/1448872/</a>"},{"pid":"14c68bf9ba387221fe036c2af345e194ee7010a2","tid":865268,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T02:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c10ffc3bed78aa1a5eefbe6614c96ffe5d89df6","tid":865268,"uid":47674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T02:07:26.000Z","msg":"撞乜撚嘢球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n桌球呀"},{"pid":"34e9ebcd2095cddbb7fd52da4740147a458f84b6","tid":865268,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re